{"tid":221382,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[星座拎]天蠍絲入","createTime":"2017-04-28T16:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T19:20:24.000Z","uid":75147,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25c55b5188c9ef307c3685b62ad3b8f5de192eac","tid":221382,"uid":75147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"識左個天蠍女大半年<br />\n一眼就鐘意左佢<br />\n跟住超主動咁追左佢三個月<br />\n但之後佢話佢有鐘意既男仔我就收埋自己無再追<br />\n<br />\n但我地繼續做朋友<br />\n有時可以好好傾，但突然又會已讀<br />\n而且唔會主動搵我<br />\n我知佢已經有男朋友，但有時講野又好似有少少曖昧<br />\n例如我話唔開心，佢會話氹返啦<br />\n又例如我講笑咁呃佢一啲野<br />\n佢又會講笑咁話要嬲之後等我道歉<br />\n<br />\n究竟你地平時都會無意間同人咁講野<br />\n定係想收兵？<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔太信星座，但如果唔用星座劃分既話咁睇一定係收兵<br />\n所以用星座劃分參考下"},{"pid":"dc2812da31a398542aa7777343cece54eec3da0a","tid":221382,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"b2b246eca39453039e2ee398ad127baf6b9a34b2","tid":221382,"uid":56552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"睇人性格"},{"pid":"4b270b515e172d5bb05573dfe8bae1d390aae3ac","tid":221382,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"天蠍 係玩曖昧嘅就手<br />\n神秘莫測"},{"pid":"123f6675d20b4cf139ba9046a407e19db97db133","tid":221382,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天蠍 係玩曖昧嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">高</span>手<br />\n神秘莫測</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d638e9595c5f17ea30cbecad148a208fd03dd47","tid":221382,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"頭三行同你一樣 我嗰個未拍拖 我準備緊一個月後同佢表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2e9f642e9059fb2e7ee21b86d11879749e4853","tid":221382,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"對你無意思 唔好諗多"},{"pid":"14aa70a03f74923fdaf2237378da9662e81ddd2b","tid":221382,"uid":75147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天蠍 係玩曖昧嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">高</span>手<br />\n神秘莫測</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但佢有男朋友喎<br />\n就算唔鐘意都會玩曖昧？"},{"pid":"053e4db5d32b5a326563fb8fbab566383382268d","tid":221382,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:23:22.000Z","msg":"天蠍就係咁仆街 <br />\n有男朋友都可以搵你日日傾電話<br />\n你自己好自為之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258d4d3e06d935989e068a2afeaa0230e73cee12","tid":221382,"uid":59065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"天蠍可以對好多人都有感覺，不過未必係鍾意"},{"pid":"0d0aa7a9ac66417553c7b0310b56fedc97baed06","tid":221382,"uid":62859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:23:54.000Z","msg":"天蠍絲表示有男友就唔會向其他男仔講曖昧野<br />\n同埋如果知道個男仔鐘意自己但自己唔鐘意<br />\n會hea覆人等人知難而退 <br />\n亦唔想俾錯signal個男仔<br />\n<br />\n利申：你個case應該唔關星座事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地有男友就唔好亂諗咁多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfa9c8626f7ee9df574d23371fd3d4819163fc7","tid":221382,"uid":75147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對你無意思 唔好諗多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係FF佢對我有意思<br />\n只係我心目中佢係一個好女仔<br />\n如果佢有男朋友都玩曖昧or收兵<br />\n我會改觀兼斬纜"},{"pid":"7b412e606973d5935f6b8c1fd5092361ac32afac","tid":221382,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>天蠍 係玩曖昧嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">高</span>手<br />\n神秘莫測</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但佢有男朋友喎<br />\n就算唔鐘意都會玩曖昧？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人都想多個人關心下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0de23bdd2484dff673f6f9d4c09408a703d5d0f","tid":221382,"uid":56552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>天蠍 係玩曖昧嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">高</span>手<br />\n神秘莫測</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但佢有男朋友喎<br />\n就算唔鐘意都會玩曖昧？</blockquote><br />\n其實人哋係咪對你係fd  利申 天蠍絲 有男友，身邊有個男仔fd都會叫到好close 唔開心會一齊傾，但完全無野，男友都知道佢既存在"},{"pid":"d6ff075c79f6bd210f837dfe899cbd7a572107df","tid":221382,"uid":10280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天蠍就係咁仆街 <br />\n有男朋友都可以搵你日日傾電話<br />\n你自己好自為之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我ex就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n派左頂帽我戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我依家諗返好撚多謝佢, 手都唔洗我分, 我又可以溝其他女了, 男人真係無野可以輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422a1a5ce788beab6cd88fe8b390ebeb15690f2e","tid":221382,"uid":75147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"可能我表達得唔清楚<br />\n我想知既係天蠍會唔會成日講曖昧野<br />\n如果呢個係你地既性格我會接受並繼續做朋友<br />\n<br />\n但如果想收兵既我就即走"},{"pid":"63901c9c37bb932a61cf20392bc84edc36849695","tid":221382,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"處女正d"},{"pid":"397728f0445640a94da6697240a30901ccc1e74b","tid":221382,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能我表達得唔清楚<br />\n我想知既係天蠍會唔會成日講曖昧野<br />\n如果呢個係你地既性格我會接受並繼續做朋友<br />\n<br />\n但如果想收兵既我就即走</blockquote><br />\n呢個應該係個人性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da81124da9a2cef5901b8497039e7e23c379687b","tid":221382,"uid":56552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能我表達得唔清楚<br />\n我想知既係天蠍會唔會成日講曖昧野<br />\n如果呢個係你地既性格我會接受並繼續做朋友<br />\n<br />\n但如果想收兵既我就即走</blockquote><br />\n我係你就直接問清楚佢"},{"pid":"06615663